# imports

## Summary

Provides an ExternalMap of Element identifiers.


## Description

Imports provides an ExternalMap of Element identifiers that are used within a document
but defined external to that document.


## Metadata

- name: imports
- Nature: ObjectProperty
- Range: ExternalMap
